author: @suanchim4147
content: I like her songs. But I also know that despite the iconoclast image she has crafted, she's really a businesswoman at heart, and a good one too. She's found the message that resonates with her fans (usually sexual expression, though she does throw in a bit of social injustice and anti-war rhetoric here and there, depending on the issue of the day) and has used it to milk them dry.
